# auto-git-commit-deepseek

a DeepSeek V3 powered VS Code extension, if you are lazy, ctrl+shift+p, input gen Commit Message , enter!

## Features

Using [DeepSeek](https://www.deepseek.com/) analyze changes, and follow [Angular commit format](https://github.com/angular/angular/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md) to genereate git commit message and push automatically

**git add .**

